TITLE: Using the database for basic operations
DESCRIPTION: Example code demonstrating how to use the drift database for basic operations like inserting data and querying tables. Shows how to instantiate the database, insert items, and retrieve them with type safety.
SOURCE: https://github.com/simolus3/drift/blob/develop/docs/docs/setup.md#2025-04-17_snippet_11

LANGUAGE: dart
