TITLE: Defining Foreign Key References in Drift
DESCRIPTION: This snippet demonstrates how to create a foreign key reference in a Drift table. It shows a 'category' column referencing the 'id' column of the 'categories' table, with update and delete actions specified.
SOURCE: https://github.com/simolus3/drift/blob/develop/docs/docs/dart_api/tables.md#2025-04-17_snippet_0

LANGUAGE: dart
CODE:
