TITLE: Updating Cart with Items in Relational Model
DESCRIPTION: Implements a transaction to update a shopping cart by replacing all its entries. First deletes all existing entries for the cart, then inserts new entries for each item in the cart.
SOURCE: https://github.com/simolus3/drift/blob/develop/docs/docs/Examples/relationships.md#2025-04-17_snippet_3

LANGUAGE: dart
CODE:
